{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To predict student GPA, Prabowo et al (2021) introduced a dual-input DL model that can handle time-series and tabular data at the same time.",
    "The model is composed of Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) for time series data and a Multi-Layer Perceptron (MLP) branch for tabular data.",
    "The database of the Student Advisory and Support Center of Bina Nusantara University contains information on 46,670 undergraduate students.",
    "The experimental findings demonstrated that the proposed model performed well with a GPA of 0.4142 MSE and 0.418 MAE.",
    "Li et al (2022) suggested an end-to-end deep learning model that predicts academic success by automatically extracting characteristics from campus-based student behavior data obtained from many sources."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "To predict student GPA, Prabowo et al (2021) introduced a dual-input DL model that can handle time-series and tabular data at the same time.",
    "Li et al (2022) suggested an end-to-end deep learning model that predicts academic success by automatically extracting characteristics from campus-based student behavior data obtained from many sources."
  ]
}